# =============================================================================
# Public snapshot allowlist
# =============================================================================
#
# Default policy: ignore every repository-root entry, then re-include only the
# files that have been reviewed as public showcase material. A new file remains
# private until it receives an explicit `!` rule below.
#
# Important: .gitignore does not remove files that are already tracked. Validate
# this policy with:
#
#   git ls-files -ci --exclude-standard
#   git status --short --ignored
#

/*


# =============================================================================
# A. Reviewed public root files
# =============================================================================

!/.dockerignore
!/.env.example
!/.gitignore
!/Dockerfile
!/LICENSE
!/README.md
!/compose.yaml
!/pyproject.toml


