# =============================================================================
# H. Intentionally private by default
# =============================================================================
#
# The root deny rule already covers these categories. They are listed here as
# policy documentation, not as additional matching rules:
#
# - data/, experiments/, runtime/, tmp/, outputs/, artifacts/ and real media;
# - cookie/, cookie-catch/, secrets, browser profiles and all credentials;
# - report/V01/, report/V02/, runs/V01/ and runs/V02/ contents;
# - project-specific seed builders and private source adapters;
# - Optmize/workflows/, Optmize/old-plan/ and unreviewed optimization drafts;
# - local manifests/path maps, IDE state, agent state, caches and virtualenvs;
# - future files under otherwise public directories until explicitly reviewed.


# =============================================================================
# I. Stage-two upload boundary (enforced rules)
# =============================================================================
#
# Sections A-G are the reviewed public allowlist. The paths below are permanent
# local-only material for this repository: do not add future `!` rules for them,
# do not stage them, and do not publish sanitized copies from these locations.
# Public documentation must instead be written as new synthetic or aggregate
# artifacts in an explicitly reviewed public path.

/Optmize/workflows/
/Optmize/old-plan/
/Optmize/阶段*.md
/Optmize/构架优化清单.md
/Optmize/项目优化方案.md
/Optmize/多线程执行提示词.md
/report/V01/Initial-screening.md
/report/V01/Manual-annotation.md
/report/V01/人工标注.md
/src/video_truthfulness/versions/v01/v01_bilibili_seed.py
/src/video_truthfulness/versions/v01/v01_bilibili_seed_frozen.py
/versions/V01/FROZEN_MANIFEST.local.json
/versions/V01/PATH_MAP.local.jsonl

# Never publish raw credentials, real run identities, private datasets, runtime
# projections, model artifacts or downloaded media from this repository.

/.agents/
/.codex/
/.tmp/
/artifacts/
/cookie/
/cookie-catch/
/data/
/experiments/
/outputs/
/registry/
/runs/V01/
/runs/V02/
/runtime/
/secrets/
/tmp/
/tools/versions/v01/cookie-catch/
*.part
*.mp4
*.mkv
*.webm
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
